{"title":"缴费相关","icon":"money","shareable":true,"id":"guide/pay/index","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":["https://publish.nenu.edu.cn/info/1068/2632.htm","https://publish.nenu.edu.cn/info/1068/2634.htm"],"content":[{"tag":"text","type":"danger","text":["报到时不需交学费和住宿费。请大家警惕谨防被骗!!!!"]},{"tag":"text","heading":"2023 年缴费时间","text":["2023年9月4日起。"]},{"tag":"title","text":"收费标准"},{"tag":"doc","name":"2023 级本科生学分学费收费标准","url":"https://assets.innenu.com/file/intro/2023-under-fee.pdf","icon":"pdf"},{"tag":"doc","name":"2023 级研究生学费标准","url":"https://assets.innenu.com/file/intro/2023-post-fee.pdf","icon":"pdf"},{"tag":"doc","name":"2024 年住宿费标准","url":"https://assets.innenu.com/file/intro/2024-dorm-fee.pdf","icon":"pdf"},{"tag":"title","text":"缴费方式"},{"tag":"text","text":["学生需要通过缴费系统自行缴费。"]},{"tag":"text","type":"note","text":["交学费这件事情不着急，在报到之后完成即可。"]},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"PC 缴费","icon":"pc","path":"guide/pay/pc"},{"text":"手机缴费","icon":"cellphone","path":"guide/pay/mobile"}]},{"tag":"text","type":"tip","heading":"申请助学贷款缴费","path":"intro/subsidize/index","text":["家庭经济困难学生可通过国家助学贷款 (校园地国家助学贷款或生源地信用助学贷款) 及时缴纳学费和住宿费。","报到后，学生可向学生资助管理中心申请校园地国家助学贷款。办理生源地信用助学贷款的学生，应及时向学院(部)反馈助学贷款相关信息，由学院 (部) 集中汇总提交学生资助管理中心。"]},{"tag":"title","text":"注意事项"},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"缴费注意事项","icon":"alert","path":"guide/pay/alert"}]}],"time":"2024 年 7 月 15 日 00:30:37"}